            "url": "https://ples.com.co",
            "label": "",
            "inlineLink": false
          },
          "description": "<p>I contributed by building a offline-first mobile app that served as a companion app for a Property Registry System for Colombian monicipalities.  It was built with Flutter and SQLite. It allowed people to save property records on low connectivity areas, and sync them back to the system once they had a stable connection to the internet.</p>",
