          },
          "description": "<p>Delivery U is an application for delivering food inside a university campus. The project aimed to develop a mobile app to help students with mobility issues and provide income opportunities for others. I developed the front-end using Flutter and MaterialDesign and I was responsible for deploying the backend and the database in Docker.</p>"
